{"type":null,"faqId":33125,"title":"开启位置服务是否会耗费数据流量？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>通常来讲，开启定位服务后，手机在使用位置相关的应用时会加载地图等数据，会消耗数据流量。建议您在使用地图等软件时，先下载好离线地图并定期在WLAN环境下更新。这样手机在使用定位服务时可最大程度地节省流量消耗。 <br>\n</span></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7827","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748505000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":31,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"位置服务,流量","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}